<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="brave-vt">brave <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /breɪv/    美 /breɪv/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>勇敢面对；冒（风险）：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Thousands braved the rain to attend the flag-raising ceremony (= attended the flag-raising ceremony even though it’s raining).
数千人冒雨参加了这次升旗仪式。</p></div></div>